@startuml DFD_Level0_Context
title Data Flow Diagram - Level 0 (Context Diagram) - Extended

entity "Student User" as StudentUser
entity "System Administrator" as Admin
entity "Tutor / Instructor" as Tutor
entity "Groq AI API" as GroqAPI
entity "MongoDB Database" as MongoDB
entity "Email & Notification Service" as EmailService
entity "Payment Gateway (Stripe)" as PaymentGateway
entity "WebRTC Media Server" as MediaServer
entity "TTS/STT Service" as SpeechService

database "Scholar Hub\nAI System" as System #CCFFFF

StudentUser --> System : Student Input Data\n(Scores, Voice, Video, Payment)
System --> StudentUser : Predictions, Explanations,\nAudio Responses, Live Streams

Tutor --> System : Schedule Sessions,\nCourse Materials, Assessments
System --> Tutor : Student Engagement Metrics,\nSession Logs

Admin --> System : System Config, API Keys,\nUser Management
System --> Admin : System Analytics, Audit Reports

System --> GroqAPI : LLM Requests (Prediction/Chat)
GroqAPI --> System : AI Generated Responses

System --> MongoDB : Read/Write Operations
MongoDB --> System : Stored Data Records

System --> EmailService : Notification Triggers
EmailService --> System : Delivery Status

System --> PaymentGateway : Payment Tokens, Amounts
PaymentGateway --> System : Transaction Status, Receipts

System --> MediaServer : Session Signaling, WebRTC Data
MediaServer --> System : Connection Status, Bandwidth Logs

System --> SpeechService : Text-to-Speech / Speech-to-Text Requests
SpeechService --> System : Audio Streams / Transcribed Text

note right of System
  Main System Processes:
  - Career Prediction & XAI
  - Conversational AI Tutoring
  - Live Session & Engagement
  - Learning & Gamification
  - Subscription & Payment
end note

@enduml
